<title>USA: Capstone files $500 mln shelf offering.</title>
<headline>Capstone files $500 mln shelf offering.</headline>
<dateline>WASHINGTON 1997-07-18</dateline>
<text>
<p>Capstone Capital Corp on Friday filed a registration with the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission for a shelf offering of up to $500 million in common shares, preferred stock, debt securities and warrants.</p>
<p>The company, a self-administered real estate investment trust, will use proceeds from the sale for general corporate purposes, which may include acquisitions and repaying outstanding debt.</p>
<p>No underwriters were named in the filing.</p>
